<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #f59f00; font-size: 22px;">Quota Limit
  Reached</h2>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #495057; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  You have reached your monthly limit for
  <strong>{{resource}}</strong>
  on the
  <strong>{{planName}}</strong>
  plan.
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #495057; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Current usage:
  <strong>{{currentUsage}}</strong>
  /
  {{limit}}
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #495057; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Upgrade your plan to continue using this feature.
</p>
<table
  role="presentation"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  style="margin: 0 auto;"
>
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #4c6ef5; border-radius: 6px;">
      <a
        href="{{frontendUrl}}/settings/billing"
        style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 28px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;"
      >Upgrade Plan</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>